      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MYOLA NICK (1) has been out of the placings at his last couple but on the winners' heels when placing three back (22.51) in a Special conditions Veteran race at Shepparton. Better than last run and makes appeal this time. CADILLAC GIRL (5) was unfancied last time out but hit the ground running to lead all the way, scoring by one length (17.85) at this track in a Other over 305m. Good beginner but will need a little luck from a middle draw. Can measure up again. PAW DAHLIA (8) finished well back at Ballarat last time when a 16 length eighth (23.10) but scored three back at Warrnambool (22.27). Must be included in calculations. RED TO BURN (2) will be hard to beat with a drop in journey.",
